   "source": [
    "# 🧠 Engram Training — GPU Accelerated\n",
    "\n",
    "Trains the Engram language model on a free Colab T4 GPU (~20-50x faster than CPU).\n",
    "When done, pushes updated weights back to GitHub automatically.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Setup required (one time)\n",
    "1. Go to **Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU**\n",
    "2. In the left sidebar click the 🔑 **Secrets** tab\n",
    "3. Add a secret named `GITHUB_TOKEN` with your GitHub personal access token\n",
    "   - Get one at: https://github.com/settings/tokens/new\n",
    "   - Scopes needed: `repo` (full)\n",
    "4. Click **Run All** (Runtime → Run all)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Cell 1: Check GPU\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "print(f'PyTorch: {torch.__version__}')\n",
    "print(f'CUDA available: {torch.cuda.is_available()}')\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print(f'GPU: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}')\n",
    "    print(f'VRAM: {torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_memory / 1e9:.1f} GB')\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print('WARNING: No GPU detected. Go to Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
